@startuml
participant "Payment Service" as PaymentService
database "Payment DB" as DB
participant "Event Bus\n(NestJS CQRS)" as EventBus

== Pha 3: Cập nhật giao dịch thành công và ghi Outbox ==

note over PaymentService: Nhánh IPN hợp lệ,\ntransaction đang pending\nvà gateway báo thanh toán thành công
activate PaymentService

PaymentService -> DB: Load Subscription và Plan\nbằng subscriptionId, planId
activate DB
DB --> PaymentService: Subscription, Plan
deactivate DB

PaymentService -> DB: Find latest active subscription\ncủa user để cộng dồn thời hạn nếu có
activate DB
DB --> PaymentService: latestActiveSub hoặc null
deactivate DB

PaymentService -> PaymentService: fulfillPayment(txn, subscription, plan, baseDate)\ntransaction='success', subscription='active'

PaymentService -> DB: Transactional save Subscription
activate DB
DB -> DB: INSERT Outbox\nSubscriptionPurchasedEvent\n(status='PENDING')
DB --> PaymentService: OK
deactivate DB

PaymentService -> DB: Transactional save Transaction\npaymentStatus='success', paidAt,\nproviderTransId, paymentMetadata
activate DB
DB --> PaymentService: OK
deactivate DB

PaymentService -> EventBus: publishAll(subscription events)
activate EventBus
EventBus --> PaymentService: Dispatch local handlers
deactivate EventBus

PaymentService -> PaymentService: subscription.commit()
deactivate PaymentService
@enduml
